11:00.910 --> 11:02.828
Is it big enough?
I wanna make sure it makes a statement.

11:02.912 --> 11:04.455
It depends. What's she like?

11:04.539 --> 11:06.707
Unlike any other woman I've ever been with.

11:07.042 --> 11:10.085
Smart, sophisticated
and for some reason she likes me.

11:10.170 --> 11:13.630
Carly, I think you should show him that
massive emerald cut in the window.

11:13.715 --> 11:16.091
- It's insane.
- How insane?

11:16.343 --> 11:17.634
It's not about the money.

11:17.719 --> 11:20.179
She's wearing this forever. I mean, hopefully.

11:20.263 --> 11:21.513
Okay.

11:21.598 --> 11:23.599
I gotta grab this. It's Terrance.

11:24.642 --> 11:26.602
- Hello.
- Vincent Chase.

11:26.728 --> 11:29.646
Mr. McQuewick,
thank you so much for calling me back.

11:29.773 --> 11:32.691
